00:41:21.856 --> 00:41:23.232
They had one hell of a day.

523
00:41:24.233 --> 00:41:26.819
Now it sounds like they're gonna
have one hell of a night.

524
00:41:31.741 --> 00:41:33.409
It's a good thing you did today.

525
00:41:34.410 --> 00:41:37.090
You broke a rule that shouldn't
have been a rule in the first place.

526
00:41:37.955 --> 00:41:39.832
And you did it for the right reasons.

527
00:41:39.916 --> 00:41:40.958
Thanks.

528
00:41:48.633 --> 00:41:50.051
Hell. should we join 'em?

529
00:41:51.260 --> 00:41:52.428
I can't.

530
00:41:53.179 --> 00:41:56.099
I never had much luck
leading men and being their friend.

531
00:41:59.477 --> 00:42:01.145
Maybe it can be different for you.

532
00:42:03.398 --> 00:42:04.565
Goodnight. son.

533
00:42:08.444 --> 00:42:10.196
<i>She brings me roses</i>

534
00:42:10.279 --> 00:42:13.366
<i>And a place to lean</i>

535
00:42:14.117 --> 00:42:17.787
<i>A drunken poet's dream</i>

